products_data.title: Didi Rose Gold Statement Earrings in Gold Dusted Glass
products_data.description: A petite interpretation of one of our favorites, the Didi Rose Gold Statement Earrings in Gold Dusted Glass are loved for their modern, weightless silhouette. At once on-trend and unexpectedly classic, these statement earrings are sure to be a staple in your wardrobe. If a chic, versatile accessory is what you're looking for, then the Didi Statement Earrings are perfect for you.

products_data.title: Thin Adjustable Chain Necklace in Rose Gold
products_data.description: Style your favorite charms on our Thin Adjustable Chain Necklace. Dainty and delicate, this charm necklace effortlessly becomes a statement when you open the custom removable bail from your Kendra Scott and attach it to the chain. The adjustable slide on this Thin Adjustable Chain Necklace makes it easy to create a length for every look.

products_data.title: Adjustable Chain Necklace in Gold

To add your favorite symbols and stones, simply open the custom removable bail on your Kendra Scott charm and attach it to the charm necklace. products_data.title: 32" Chain Link Necklace in Rose Gold
products_data.description: Share your style story with our 32" Chain Link Necklace. Thanks to its subtly hammered finish, this long charm necklace has a sophisticated vintage feel to it. To add your favorite charms to the 32" Chain Link Necklace, simply open the custom removable bail that comes with every Kendra Scott charm, attach, and snap close.
